column1: There are many entries where hi_wc is the same as humid, which is probably from human error. Seems correlated with E DeLeon entries.
On 7/25/2023, a "G. Guzman" appears before "Guzman," so they're probably the same person
12:30 a.m. temp on 7/26/2023 noted with a percent sign
Two numbers placed for wind from 2:30-4:30 on 7/26/2023
"Dp69" added with temp on 7/28/2023 from 10:30-11:30 p.m. Also used for the majority in temp values on 7/29/2023
wind in wrong column from 12:30-5:30 a.m. on 7/29/2023
hi_wc values crossed out from 6:30-9:30 a.m. on 7/29/2023
"Jones S" and "Jones" are probably the same person, but he or she signed differently starting on 7/29/2023
"Garcia" and "M. Garcia" are probably different people because they have different handwriting
